"title": "5969: treachery",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5969: treachery",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>A betrayal of trust by a close companion, often involving a preconceived plan. Those found guilty of treachery are severely punished by God.</p>\n<h2>Treachery against God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph3:4\">ZEP 3:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev26:40\">LEV 26:40</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa48:8\">ISA 48:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa59:13\">ISA 59:13</a></p>\n<h2>Treachery against other people</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam20:9-2Sam20:10\">2SA 20:9–20:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg16:19\">JDG 16:19</a> <em>Delilah against Samson</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam18:17\">1SA 18:17</a> <em>Saul against David</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam3:27\">2SA 3:27</a> <em>Joab against Abner</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam4:6\">2SA 4:6</a> <em>Recab and Baanah against Ish-Bosheth</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam11:15\">2SA 11:15</a> <em>David against Uriah</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam13:28-2Sam13:29\">2SA 13:28–13:29</a> <em>Absalom against Amnon</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs21:7-1Kgs21:13\">1KI 21:7–21:13</a> <em>Jezebel against Naboth</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh6:2\">NEH 6:2</a> <em>Sanballat and Geshem against Nehemiah</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth3:8\">EST 3:8</a> <em>Haman against Mordecai</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:49\">MAT 26:49</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:45\">MRK 14:45</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:47-Luke22:48\">LUK 22:47–22:48</a> <em>Judas against Jesus Christ</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts7:18-Acts7:19\">ACT 7:18–7:19</a> <em>Pharaoh against the Israelites</em></p>\n<h2>Punishment of the treacherous</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:18\">ACT 1:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam18:14-2Sam18:15\">2SA 18:14–18:15</a> <em>Absalom</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs2:31-1Kgs2:34\">1KI 2:31–2:34</a> <em>Joab</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs9:30-2Kgs9:37\">2KI 9:30–9:37</a> <em>Jezebel</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth7:10\">EST 7:10</a> <em>Haman</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps25:3\">PSA 25:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps59:5\">PSA 59:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa33:1\">ISA 33:1</a></p>\n<h2>Treachery in the purposes of God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:27-Acts4:28\">ACT 4:27–4:28</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen50:20\">GEN 50:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg9:22-Judg9:24\">JDG 9:22–9:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs9:23\">2KI 9:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs11:14\">2KI 11:14</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr23:13\">2CH 23:13</a></p>",
